Communicated by:
ProMED from HealthMap Alerts

[There are not enough clear symptoms listed in this report to speculate on what caused the students to feel unwell. Only dizziness and vomiting are mentioned.

The article indicates the illness may have been related to one or more substances added to water or some other form of drink. It may have been too much alcohol as well. There are not enough clinical signs to speculate on the intoxication at this point. ProMED would appreciate information about this incident from knowledgeable sources.

We do wish the affected individuals a speedy recovery. - Mod.TG

